title: Evolve-CODEX

C O D E X

                             Evolve (c) 2K

   Release Date :  2/2015                        Protection : Steam
   Discs        :  1                             Genre      : Action


   Evolve is the winner of over 60 awards making it the  most  award
   winning game coming in 2015.  Most notably,Evolve  is  the  first
   game to win both the official E3 and Gamescom Best of Show awards
   in the same year. In a savage world of  man vs  nature,  are  you
   the hunter or the hunted? Turtle Rock Studios bring  you  Evolve,
   the next-generation of multiplayer shooters  where  four  hunters
   face-off against a single, player-controlled monster.

   - Burn or mount the .iso
   - Run setup.exe and install
   - Copy crack from CODEX dir to installdir
   - Play
